desc_long							评测						“... there are jokes that are simply unacceptable.”1/10 – Илья Мэддисон“What is he saying? Vodka worth 3.50”- – Виктор Зуев“For local stall? In the 80? Just ***. ***! Now, that's a stall that behind him, I was in Moscow being, that is, Muscovites! I saw well, year, well, so that it was possible to go to any, well, year 94, 95, 96, well here to with such a variety, it is the year 96. Prior to that, either in the street or at markets, the so-called , here. And so just like that tents have sprung up everywhere, everywhere, everywhere, this year really 96, especially with such a range, over there Adrenaline Rush can see, it is generally the 2000s !!! Well, in short, the guys do not bother.”- – Виктор Зуев												关于这款游戏							Spakoyno is a Russian visual novel set in the late USSR. This is a story of an average Russian guy named Kirill. The characters are left at the borderline conflict of old and new society. High crime rates, corruption and a change of morals… Can he survive the new society?The brother of the protagonist has gone into criminal underground and the father spends all his time at work and can't protect his sons. Militsiya doesn't do anything about local criminal groups. Kirill is left alone… Everyone is against him: Kirill doesn't favor neither patriots, nor bandits or soviet conservatives. He wishes for peace in our world, so he decides to struggle.						
title	 Spakoyno: Back to the USSR 2.0			
